description:
This meet up is for group of ten, wine tasting will last 45 minutes, and afterwards there is a possibility to continue and have a drink together during a networking event given in the same building.

The wine tasting is given by a professional sommelier with a different theme for each session.
name: Wine discovery and enjoyment as well as a great social time!
